Class SimpleHashtable<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw5.collections.SimpleHashtable<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - key of the given item
    V - value of the given item
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Hashtable<K,V>, java.lang.Iterable<SimpleHashtable.TableEntry<K,V>>

    public class SimpleHashtable<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Hashtable<K,V>, java.lang.Iterable<SimpleHashtable.TableEntry<K,V>>
    Hashtable implementation that uses TableEntry as it's building block. Stores lists of SimpleHashtable.TableEntry in an array.

    Juraj Pejnovic
